tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE vpn_session_logs (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  user_id INT,
  ip_address VARCHAR(15),
  duration INT,
  data_usage INT
)

CREATE TABLE vpn_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    data_usage INT
);

CREATE TABLE vpn_user_sessions (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  duration INTERVAL,
  status VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE vpn_gateway_sessions (
  gateway_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  duration INTERVAL,
  status VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE vpn_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    login_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    logout_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES vpn_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE vpn_traffic_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT NOT NULL,
    logging_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    traffic_amount INT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES vpn_sessions(session_id)
);

CREATE TABLE vpn_errors (
    error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT NOT NULL,
    error_message VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    error_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES vpn_sessions(session_id)
);
